    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with proactive rod bearing replacement using ACL shells and ARP bolts, alongside refreshed throttle actuators. The 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, coupled with an M Variable Differential Lock that remains silent and responsive. The factory Alpine White paint shows no signs of road rash or swirling, and the underside is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), the suspension geometry and bushings are in factory-new condition, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability this chassis is renowned for. A true turnkey masterpiece for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
