    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, preserved by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition. The premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent, with zero bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively by certified master technicians. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. With exceptionally low mileage and a clean title in hand, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
